snippet.description:
Stranger Things 5, which premieres with VOL 1 — November 26, 5pm PT* VOL 2 — Christmas, 5pm PT* THE FINALE — New Year’s Eve, 5pm PT*

SUBSCRIBE: https://bit.ly/SlisTeaser

About SlisTeaser:
SlisTeaser create trailer mashups—also known as recut trailers—by combining scenes from one or more movies to craft new, imaginative trailers.
These fan-made edits often reimagine a film’s genre or storyline, offering a fresh perspective on familiar footage.
Due to their transformative nature, these mashups are protected under Fair Use as parody, adding creative spin and anticipation for fans and upcoming releases.

Stranger Things 5: Final Season | Trailer | One Last Time | Netflix

The Hawkins crew are finally back together as they brace for their toughest challenge yet. With the town under military quarantine and Vecna unleashing fresh nightmares on our heroes, the stakes aren’t just raised — they’ve been turned Upside Down in this fifth and final season.

Tryna free my mind before the end of the world

Si tiene que doler
Eso de haber perdido 
Al amor de mi vida
El dolor es bienvenido

No es para menos
Vean quién se me fue

Es donde quiero estar 
Déjenme disfrutar mi sufrimiento

Y si me ven vulnerable, así es 
Que se me note que no te olvidé
Y si preguntan que cómo me va
